text: Desmiphora xerophila is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 1995. It is known from Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora xerophila. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1995
